description: Pop culture creates waves of fresh, innovative ideas & concepts every day. From viral videos to entertainment trends, it seems like every minute we witness a new phenomenon makes its way to the scene and create a lasting impression on our lives forever. The latest sensation to sweep the streets of California is Hollywood On Fleek™.Unlike any other food truck in the city, Hollywood On Fleek™ delivers gourmet All-American classics with an urban edge to the entire city of Los Angeles & surrounding areas. With menu specialties like the mouth-watering "Open Face Steak Sandwich" and Surf and Turf Fries, HOF is all about great vibes and great eats, at even greater prices.Pop culture evolves and caters to the lifestyles of the people. It's time that your new favorite food truck does the same.
name: Hollywood On Fleek
